      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/3/32/2",
      "text": [
        " \"يُشْبِعُ بَطْنَهَا وَ يَكْسُو جُثَّتَهَا وَ إِنْ جَهِلَتْ غَفَرَ لَهَا\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4526 - Ishaq ibn Ammar asked Abu Abdillah (as) about the right of a woman over her husband.\nImam (as) said: \"He should satisfy her hunger, clothe her body, and if she acts ignorantly, he should forgive her.\""
        ]
      }
